Sentencas: Local distribution of oxide ionic flows was visualized at the cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat tube Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs) stacks under operating condition.
Titulo: Visualization of oxide ionic diffusion at cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat-tube SOFC cells-stack

Sentencas: Isotope labeling (O-18 labeling) technique and secondary ion mass spectrometry (SIMS) analysis enabled us to visualize the trace of O-18 diffusion through the (La,Sr)FeO3 cathode/CeO2 interlayer/YSZ electrolyte interfaces in a frozen state.
Titulo: Visualization of oxide ionic diffusion at cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat-tube SOFC cells-stack

Sentencas: The difference of O-18 intensity was observed at (La,Sr)FeO3 cathode as well as CeO2 interlayer among different cells.
Titulo: Visualization of oxide ionic diffusion at cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat-tube SOFC cells-stack

Sentencas: This difference can come from the surface O-16/O-18 exchange rates of (La,Sr)FeO3 cathode and the amounts of O-18(2) supplied to cells.
Titulo: Visualization of oxide ionic diffusion at cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat-tube SOFC cells-stack

Sentencas: Local difference of O-18 intensity suggested the local distribution of oxide ionic currents at different cells in the stack.
Titulo: Visualization of oxide ionic diffusion at cathode/interlayer/electrolyte interfaces in real flat-tube SOFC cells-stack
